2026-05-19T04:01:20.8727188Z 273            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-19T04:01:20.8727515Z 274            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-19T04:01:20.8727737Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-19T04:01:20.8728104Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-19T04:01:20.8728436Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-19T04:01:20.8728940Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
